Professional XML dynamic intro 03

You just have to edit the info.xml !!


here is a example : 

<Info>
<Text1><![CDATA[UNIQUE <b>CREATIVE</b> DESIGN]]></Text1>
<Text2><![CDATA[ULTIMATE <b>WORKS</b>]]></Text2>
<Text3><![CDATA[SIMPLY <b>PHENOMENAL</b>]]></Text3>
<Text4><![CDATA[COMPETITIVE <b>ADVANTAGES</b>]]></Text4>
<Text5><![CDATA[OUTSTANDING <b>RESULTS</b>]]></Text5>
<Text6><![CDATA[<b>SEE</b> THE DIFFERENCE]]></Text6>
<Text7><![CDATA[WE <b>EMPORER</b> YOUR BUSINESS]]></Text7>
<Text8><![CDATA[TO THE <b>NEXT LEVEL</b>]]></Text8>
<Slogan><![CDATA[COMPANY <b>SLOGAN</b>]]></Slogan>
<CompanyName><![CDATA[COMPANY <b>NAME</b>]]></CompanyName>

<ButtonText><![CDATA[ENTER<b> WEBSITE</b>]]></ButtonText>
<SkipText><![CDATA[SKIP INTRO >]]></SkipText>
<Link>http://www.flashden.net/user/FlashBros</Link>
</Info>

XML DESCRIPTION :

<Text1> : 1st line of the in the intro.
<Text2> : 2nd line of text in the intro.
<Text3> : 3th line of text in the intro.
<Text4> : 4th line of text in the intro.
<Text5> : 5th line of text in the intro.
<Text6> : 6th line of text in the intro.
<Text7> : 7th line of text in the intro.
<Text8> : 8th line of text in the intro.
<Slogan> : slogan of the company.
<CompanyName> : Last line of text, the company name.
<ButtonText> : The text on the button at the end of the intro.
<Link> : Where the intro will be redirected.
<SkipText> : Text for the skip button.

P.S : <![CDATA[ is Used to support of <b> tags(html tag).

Just change all the info in the xml and it will work.

If you want to edit stuff manually in the intro, everything is named and easy to edit.

Don't forget to always have the .AS classes in the same folder of your .fla project. Same with the caurina folder.
Caurina folder is the classes for Tweener(http://code.google.com/p/tweener/).

If you want to modify the font, open the fla and change in the library the introFont Font object. Also, if you want to support Bold tag, change on the first frame, on the label FONT, the textfield with the correct font and style.